\endverbatim

To connect to azure, the arguments can look like:

    streetlightd --application=forwarder --presentation=json --session=azure-amqp --host=<iot hub name>.azure-devices.net --user=<device name> --password=<device key>

`streetlightd` accesses the D-Bus object `ch.bbv.streetlight`.
Ensure that some service is providing it before `streetlightd` is started.

# session-test

The application `session-test` is used to test or debug a session or connection to a server.

